comment: Lowry (TOR) hooks Winslow (MIA) affecting his ability to defend the drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) makes incidental contact with Patterson (TOR) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Biyombo (TOR) and Winslow (MIA) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Carroll (TOR) makes contact with Johnson's (MIA) arm that affects his shot attempt.
DeRozan (TOR) gathers the ball and then picks up his pivot foot up when he jumps.
Patterson (TOR) and Johnson (MIA) engage under the rim.
Winlsow (MIA) and Carroll (TOR) engage briefly and separate.
Carroll (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Wade (MIA) that does not affect his RSBQ on the drive.
Johnson (MIA) makes body contact with Joseph (TOR) during his shot attempt.
Toronto does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
[Observable in enhanced video] Wade (MIA) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Wade (MIA) maintains legal guarding position as Patterson (TOR) drives to the basket.
Johnson (MIA) maintains legal guarding position on DeRozan's (TOR) drive. DeRozan looses the ball before any contact.
Johnson (MIA) sets the screen on Joseph (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Carroll (TOR) makes contact with Dragic's (MIA) body that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Carroll (TOR) makes contact with Deng's (MIA) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) maintains a legal guardng position when defending Carroll's (TOR) drive to the rim.
The ball comes to rest on the basket flange, resulting in a jump ball between any two players at center circle.
Wade (MIA) makes contact with Ross (TOR) that affects his FOM away from the ball.
Deng (MIA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Carroll (TOR) makes contact with Dragic's (MIA) head that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Joseph (TOR) attempts a take foul on Wade (MIA), who avoids any material contact.
